	Device/Audiotron version 1.01
	===============================
	
DESCRIPTION

   Device::Audiotron provides a tie-in into the API included in the
   latest firmware for Turtle Beach's Audiotron.
   

DEPENDENCIES

   LWP 5.64


INSTALLATION

   To install this module type the following:

      perl Makefile.PL
      make
      make test
      make install


CHANGES

    See the Changes file for more details


